title: PTE Patch 5.0 + Stadium pack + adboard pack [for PES 2016]
description:
*** PTE Patch 5.0 + Stadium pack + adboard pack [for PES 2016] ***



*** What's new ***
- Added Kobenhavn, Club Brugge, Rubin Kazan, Spartak Moskva, PAOK, Skenderbeu, Steaua Bucuresti - Fully licensed with correct squads, lineups, kits, faces, stats & acessories.
- Imported all the transfers, new players and tactics from the PES Live Update (March 17)
- BrasileirÃ£o 2016  - Added Botafogo, E.C. Vitoria, America Mineiro & Santa Cruz
- Primera Division Argentina 2016 - Added Atletico Tucuman & Patronato
- New/Updated kits for: PSG and Eintracht Frankfurt 
- Added Malaysia & Indonesia national teams
- Ethiad Stadium (Manchester City) added
- Updated the Liga BBVA Bancomer
- Updated managers for all teams
- Added 40 + new faces, including for: Zidane, Ronaldo, Beckham, Rashford, Mayoral, etc.
- Fixed accessories, shirt names, positions, etc for a lot of players
- Removed all the new duplicated players from Data Pack 3.0
- Added new balls, including: argentum AFA 2016, Ordem3 CBF 2016
- Added new boots, including: Messi 15, Mercurial Superfly CR7 Natural Diamond, Nike Radiant Reveal Pack
- Added new gloves, including: Adidas Ace Zones Pro (different colors), Nike Premier SGT, Nike Vapor Grip, Puma evoSPEED 1.4, etc.
- KONAMI Data Pack 3.0 & KONAMI Patch 1.04.00 included
- Online Compatible
